TEXT.TITLE: FEDERAL EXPRESS <FDX> FEBRUARY VOLUME RISES
TEXT.BODY: Federal Express Corp said February package and document volume was 14.7 mln, up 26.0 pct from 11.6 mln a year earlier. The company said year-to-date volume was 128.9 mln, up from 100.2 mln a year before. Reuter
